
Noxim 
----------------------------------

To compile (first time):

1) Edit Makefile.defs according to your systemc path installation
2) make (don't mind about warning messages)

Note 1: If you are using SystemC 2.2, please set to DISABLE the
SC_SIGNAL_WRITE_CHECK enviroment variable before compiling.

bash: export SC_SIGNAL_WRITE_CHECK=DISABLE
csh: setenv SC_SIGNAL_WRITE_CHECK DISABLE

Alternatively, under bash, you can type

source sourceme

